 *
 * @return
 *  - LE_OK             Function succeeded.
 *  - LE_BAD_PARAMETER  A parameter is invalid.
 *  - LE_OVERFLOW       The Recipient Address length exceeds the length of the provided buffer.
 *  - LE_FAULT          Function failed.
 */
